4th Evo Eco PhD Meeting

Lutherstadt Wittenberg, 04.-06.03.2020




Organised by Rolff group, Armitage group and McMahon group

We are pleased to announce that the 4th Evo Eco PhD Student Meeting will be hosted by the Freie University Berlin, with invited speakers Peter Hammerstein, Stuart Wikby and Charlotte Rafaluk-Mohr
